Global OTC Health and Wellness Products Market Insights
OTC Health and Wellness Products Market size was valued at USD 80 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 120 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.5% from 2024 to 2030.

OTC Health and Wellness Products Market Overview
The global OTC Health and Wellness Products market was valued at USD 350.1 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 457.9 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.1% during the forecast period. This growth can be attributed to increasing consumer awareness of health, a rise in self-medication trends, and the accessibility of OTC products through online platforms. The market is also seeing significant growth due to the convenience, affordability, and effectiveness of these products. The rise of preventive healthcare measures and natural, organic health products is also driving market expansion.

